5. The output must remain syntactically valid code and maintain the original folder/file structure.
6. Do not invent or add missing code â€” only summarize what exists.
7. Separate the output clearly for each file to retain per-file context.

Workspace content:
${workspaces}
    `
});


var data = {
  openai: { 
    json: {
      model: "gpt-4o-mini",
